# Runtime state (all stored outside the plugin dir under ~/.claude/)
# Included here as a reminder — these paths are never inside this repo:
#   ~/.claude/channels/nfty/channels.json   channel store
#   ~/.claude/channels/nfty/secrets.json    encryption + signing keys (chmod 600)
#   ~/.claude/nfty/pending/                 pending reply records
#   ~/.claude/nfty/audit/                   non-repudiation audit log (v0.4)
